{"id":301951,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/【图说天朝】不要碾死我/","date":"2013-07-03T01:23:24Z","modified":"2013-10-05T00:16:10Z","title":"【图说天朝】不要碾死我","content":"<p>6月30日下午13点30分许，河南荥阳市发生一起车祸，被撞的女子被卡在车轮下，连声喊疼，并央求“不要碾死我”。当时，一名网友开车经过，看见一辆从小巷往大路上拐的电动车，被一辆车牌号为豫A-G2798的红色大型水泥罐车“咣”的一声碾到轮下，拍下全程。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/07/92QKI3H600AP0001.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-301952\" alt=\"92QKI3H600AP0001\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/07/92QKI3H600AP0001.jpg\" width=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/07/92QKI3H600AP0001.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/07/92QKI3H600AP0001-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[9233]}